import React from 'react'; const about = (

Hi, I'm Ross!

I am a Software Engineer for Togetherwork - a company based out of Brooklyn, NY that provides group management and payment software for groups and organizations in the United States and Canada. I work on the payment processing team where my main duties involve: maintaining our payment platform API, adding new features to our front-end reporting application, and providing support to our team of Business Analysts.

Outside of work, I enjoy spending time with my family and our dogs, Walter and Trista. Some of my other hobbies include: riding motorcycles, music and movies, making coffee for my team at work, and enjoying a nice beer - I like stouts and IPAs.

); export default about;
